{"tid":568600,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台北討論","createTime":"2018-02-22T02:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T08:55:49.000Z","uid":84115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"253efb75603d3f8861f7d42212601edfe1bc7ee8","tid":568600,"uid":84115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"小弟黎緊3月會同屋企人去台北遊<br />\n大緻去邊都計劃左<br />\n<br />\n第1日 預計14:00 到達台北 午餐並酒店check in後大約 15:00<br />\n第2日 淡水<br />\n第3日 九份&amp;十份<br />\n第4日 陽明山<br />\n第5日 宜蘭<br />\n第6日 周圍行街買野 18:00 機回香港<br />\n<br />\n主要行程如上, 每日一個主要地點 餘下時間到周圍悠閒行街<br />\n但唯獨第1日 諗唔掂 check in完已經15:00 得返半日唔夠時間 去邊到好?(酒店位於西門町附近)<br />\n巴打們有冇好推介? 同埋對我以上行程有任何意見都可以提出 (第1次100%自己計劃行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"5d4892afae2aff8f269ed7445da4955e91b3eec6","tid":568600,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:11:03.000Z","msg":"如果我排就宜蘭最前<br />\n唔放最後係避免交通上有乜差池<br />\n都可以盡量降低個影響"},{"pid":"44a89ba9f92a267f684e229f05aa348d0f56ba23","tid":568600,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n但唯獨第1日 諗唔掂 check in完已經15:00 得返半日唔夠時間 去邊到好?(酒店位於西門町附近)<br />\n巴打們有冇好推介? 同埋對我以上行程有任何意見都可以提出 (第1次100%自己計劃行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n亦正係咁原因，我會d1直入宜蘭，留一晚，整返個溫泉或夜市（視乎你屋企人選擇）。d2上午至中午可輕鬆遊少少宜蘭先返台北市。<br />\n<br />\n來回台北市到宜蘭客運約45分鐘車程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208437f4f45290b56a3d8f5e09fb2e3e3700df34","tid":568600,"uid":36034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"九份十份太過遊客區個人覺得<br />\n上個月我去左八斗子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/003212_9c359221df2f1c0a9508b9f4290bc5ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F003212_9c359221df2f1c0a9508b9f4290bc5ff.png&h=064642dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/003220_90c0f97fb7fc882d34d079b9b732d418.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F003220_90c0f97fb7fc882d34d079b9b732d418.png&h=6c0594a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/003225_1f8098e22a273fd35dbc75c931377963.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F003225_1f8098e22a273fd35dbc75c931377963.png&h=326cc9f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/003234_c9e0266ab936bb7a5eff15acfd099aef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F003234_c9e0266ab936bb7a5eff15acfd099aef.png&h=a2344a6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0595fc736af31838f0d0ae0fb70a6bb2c668db00","tid":568600,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:53:15.000Z","msg":"有時間可以去下崩瓦咖啡店 我細佬開的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057f570db76a4cdf71bf59d0e242b71d5af69ed6","tid":568600,"uid":171257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"九份可以去爬茶壺山<br />\n黃金博物館可以淘金"}]}